<P>
   On a more discouraging note, Unisys dropped nearly 20 percent,
falling $2.813 a share to $11.313 after the struggling computer
systems company posted disappointing results.
</P>
<P>
   Health insurance stocks fell sharply after Aetna issued a
warning that its second-quarter results would come in well below
analyst expectations. Shares of Aetna were down $8.75 at $57.875, a
loss of 13 percent.
</P>
<P>
   Overseas, Japan's Nikkei stock average fell 1.98 percent,
Germany's DAX index fell 0.32 percent, Britain's FT-SE 100 fell
1.15 percent, and France's CAC-40 fell 1.58 percent.
</P>
