<HEADLINE> Tigers Place Juan Gonzalez on DL  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   DETROIT (AP) -- Juan Gonzalez, out with a sore left ankle, was
placed on the 15-day disabled list by the Detroit Tigers on
Tuesday, retroactive to July 8.
</P>
<P>
   Gonzalez, batting .284 with 13 homers and 35 RBIs, has missed 24
of Detroit's 90 games due to a variety of injuries this season, but
this was the first time he has gone on the disabled list since
